I will provide 1 Week of FREE Support after Order Completion (Post-delivery)


Hey there,

Why choose me?

  4. Will make sure the outcome is efficient and fulfills the needs
  5. Rest, talk with me to gain my trust!


Let's connect and discuss your requirements! I will also come-up with best offer for you, for your needs, UNDER YOUR BUDGET!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you edit or customize existing plugin?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can troubleshoot or debug and also customize any existing plugin. I can also fix any of your Wordpress issues you have.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you develop a fresh plugin for our custom needs?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, this is what the gig is for. I will create, design and develop a fresh plugin as per your requirement. Once done, you will get a plugin file which you can upload on wordpress and install it which will fulfill your requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long does it take to receive the completed custom WordPress plugin?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The delivery time (time-frame or timeline) for your custom WordPress plugin depends on its complexity and my current workload (ongoing orders). I will provide you with a timeframe when you place your order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide post-delivery support?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do provide support even after the order deliver or order completion. On all the plans, I provide 1 week free support after the delivery. You can contact me for assistance.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you integrate the custom WordPress plugin with other existing plugins on my website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, the custom WordPress plugin can be integrated with other existing plugins on your website. Please provide details of the plugins you want the custom plugin to work with during the ordering process.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will the custom WordPress plugin be compatible with future WordPress updates?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I strive to develop custom WordPress plugins that are compatible with future WordPress updates. I always follow the Coding Standards and Best Practices. However, in case any compatibility issues arise, I offer support to ensure the plugin functions properly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I request additional features or modifications to the custom WordPress plugin after delivery?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I am open to discussing additional features or modifications to the custom WordPress plugin after the initial delivery. However, it may involve an additional cost and timeframe depending on the complexity of the requested changes. In case you need help/support, you can reach out to me directly.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you develop a custom WordPress plugin based on my design or specifications?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can develop a custom WordPress plugin based on your design or specifications. Please message me and provide detailed information about your requirements, including any design mockups or specifications you have. We can discuss everything beforehand to make sure you receive satisfactory result.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I use the custom WordPress plugin on multiple websites?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you can use the plugin developed on as many websites as you want. Make sure to share with me your primary intent of using the plugin, whether the commercial or personal use.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I sell the custom WordPress plugin that you develop for me?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Depends. Please message me so we can discuss whether you intend to use the WordPress plugin for personal use only or if you also require the commercial rights to sell the plugin. Based on your preference, I will provide you with the appropriate licensing terms and ensure that your needs are met.
